<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xìn niàn yǒng bù néng bèi jiāng hé zǔ gé 迦南983</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xìn niàn yǒng bù néng bèi jiāng hé zǔ gé, shǐ mìng yǒng bù néng bèi jù lí zǔ lán.
 shén de ér nǚ zǒng shì yào xiàng qián, bǎ zhǔ ài sā biàn rén jiān.
 nǐ zǒu dào biān sāi, wǒ zǒu dào shēn shān.
 yán zhe shān lù wān wān, yuè mò dù qiān. xiǎo xiǎo máo wū xī shuǐ chán chán,
 fú yīn zhī huǒ yǒng bù miè. shén de ér nǚ chù chù zài diǎn rán.
 shēng mìng zhī hé yī dìng yào liú biàn, shǔ yú shén de měi yī gè jiā yuán.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>983</hymn_number>
</song>